{{Infobox adult biography | name = Hallvard Aamlid | birth_name = | birth_date = 25 January 1973 | birth_place = | death_date = | death_place = | nationality = Norwegian | spouse = | height = | weight = | ethnicity = | alias = | number_of_films = | website = }} '''Hallvard Aamlid''' (born 25 January 1973) is a Norwegian politician for the [[Liberal Party of Norway|Liberal Party]].
He served as a deputy representative to the [[Stortinget|Norwegian Parliament]] from [[Oslo]] during the term 1997–2001.
Outside politics he works for the publishing house [[Universitetsforlaget]].
