'''R. R. "Roy" van Aalst''' ({{IPA-nl|ɛr ɛr rɔj vɑn aːlst}}; born 28 March 1983) is a [[Netherlands|Dutch]] [[politician]]. He has been a member of the [[House of Representatives (Netherlands)|House of Representatives]] representing the [[Party for Freedom]] since 23 March 2017 and a member of the [[States of Overijssel]] since March 2015.<ref>"[https://www.parlement.com/id/vkaqasbcluh2/r_r_roy_van_aalst R.R. (Roy) van Aalst]" (in Dutch), ''Parlement & Politiek''. Retrieved 15 April 2017.</ref> Van Aalst is married, has two children, and lives in [[Hengelo]].<ref>"[https://www.pvvoverijssel.nl/index.php/statenleden/roy-van-aalst Roy van Aalst]" (in Dutch), ''[[Party for Freedom]] Overijssel''. Retrieved 15 April 2017.</ref>
